	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et vitae innocentiam a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Negotia hactenus obstiterunt, quominus scripserim, at nunc paucis ad singula<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Nämlich im Brief von <persName ref="person154">Myconius</persName> an ihn, 20. Juli 1533, oben <ref target="file10275">Nr. 244</ref>.</note> respondebo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video autem nimis verum esse, quod trito fertur proverbio, de calamitosis inauspicatissima quaeque narrari semper<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Etwa im Sinne des deutschen Sprichwortes: «Wer Unglück hat, braucht für Spott nicht zu sorgen.»</note>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Calamitosi sane sumus, sed non in iis, quae impinguntur nobis.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam certa spes est nostros nihil negotii cum Gallo habituros.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="167"/>Cur autem nuper<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">nuper <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> receperint nuncii nostri viri alias boni coronatos aliquot, et quid praeterea actum sit super eo negotio<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Siehe oben S. 164, 10f.</note>, procul dubio non nescis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam quod de advenis et exulibus et profugis urbe et agro expellendis narrasti, longe alio instituto coeptum<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">coeptum <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> est, quod lator<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Unbekannt.</note> praesentium exponet.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quodsi praeterea adversum <placeName ref="place121">Bern[enses]</placeName> a nostris quidpiam<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c">quidpiam <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> institui coepit, universi nescimus, nec timemus quidpiam posse institui.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ager enim totus, denique cives universi <placeName ref="place121">Bernatibus</placeName> melius volunt, quam ut paucorum (quam tamen nescimus) conspiratio nocere possit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libros nostros olim adversus catabaptistas<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">«Von dem unverschämten Frevel der Wiedertäufer», 1531 (HBBibl I 28).</note> rudi Minerva<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Mit roher Hand oder derbem Verstand, vgl. Adagia, 1, 1, 37 (LB II 42); Otto 224, Nr. 1119.</note> conscriptos mitto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName ref="person132">Lavatero</persName><note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="person1479">Heinrich Lavater</persName>, s. oben S. 157, 28f.</note> non est, quod aliud expectes.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Manebit adhuc apud me.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Egit tamen gratias <persName ref="person132">Lavaterus</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="person132">Hans Rudolf Lavater</persName>, s. ebenda.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non desperamus, de gratia domini subinde meliora speramus.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Semel humiliavit dominus, exaltabit denuo<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Vgl. Mt 23, 12; Jak 4, 10.</note>, si illi fuerit visum, quamquam nullam exaltationem cupiamus, quam quae tyrannidi quorundam eximeret.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed fiat voluntas domini<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10">Vgl. Mt 6, 10.</note>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orato pro nobis dominum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri, 18. augusti 1533.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person1479">Heinrychus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Lieber, habend ir gewüsse bottschaff[t] gen Burgis inn Franckrych, so lassend michs wüssen; so wölltend wir unsernn knaben<note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11"><persName ref="person79">Konrad Geßner</persName> und <persName ref="person69">Johannes Fries</persName>, die seit April 1533 in <placeName ref="place165">Bourges</placeName> studierten, s. oben <ref target="file10241">Nr. 210</ref> und 224.</note> gällt rüsten, inen ze schickenn.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="person154">Oswaldo Myconio</persName>, <placeName ref="place97">Basileiensis</placeName> ecclesiae praesuli vigilantissimo, fratri in domino observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
